description: Sunny 3BD/2.5BA Southie duplex with garage parking! Enter into an open living/kitchen/dining with an abundance of natural light, gas fireplace and hardwood floors. Sliders off the living room lead you to your private deck with direct access to your private patio, making it the perfect entertaining spot. The kitchen showcases granite countertops, custom shaker cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, large island and wine fridge. A spacious primary suite boasts a large walk in closet as well as an en-suite with double marble vanity and frameless glass step-in shower, with rain head shower. The lower level includes two additional large bedrooms with ample closet space & another full bath. Additional amenities include; in-unit laundry, garage parking, central A/C and abundant storage throughout. Close to the amazing restaurants and shops in Southie this is one you don’t want to miss!
